      "_value": "Find #p218# in #m10001050#."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "Under the watchtower in #m10001050#, you see Pia, wearing a teddy bear costume. How cute! She tells you that she ran into a bully #o16# on her way to #m10002000#, and now she wants you to show the rude mushroom who's boss! Collect #b20 #t4000013#s and 20 #t4000016#s#k as proof. You contemplate telling Pia she's asking to be teased, walking around the forest in a bear costume, but you decide against it."
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "You delivered #b20 #t4000013#s and 20 #t4000016#s#k to Pia in #m10001050#. She was thrilled that she got vengeance on the mushrooms and gave you a Scroll for hat. All you have to do is click on it in the Use tab of your Item Inventory and drag it to your helmet in the Equipment window... Oh, and you'll have to cross your fingers and hope the Scroll doesn't fail."
    },
    "demandSummary": {
      "_dirName": "demandSummary",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#i4000013:# #t4000013:# #c4000013# / 20\\r\\n#i4000016:# #t4000016:# #c4000016# / 20"
